{"tid":1624341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廣傳】破解政府陰謀方法","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T03:41:10.000Z","uid":274045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8dcc0d155179c592f3077fc5c4195bdad9034b","tid":1624341,"uid":274045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"尋日多區行動，而警方故意唔出現，就係想屈我地好似721班黑社會一樣，名正言順地話我地四處破壞，影響社會。從而逆轉民意<br />\n<br />\n破解方法很簡單:<br />\n<br />\n只要展示我地<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">賞罰分明</span></strong></span></strong>就可以<br />\n<br />\n做法:<br />\n<br />\n1.全力破壞親中店鋪<br />\n<br />\n2.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">向黃店及外資商店獻花再大肆宣傳</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有2大好處<br />\n<br />\n1.證明我地同班無差別打人黑社會唔同，同班垃圾警察有法不依，有法不執唔同。我地有8成民意，只要有合理辯解，基本上唔會翻盤同做咩都得。<br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">形成社會風氣，去黃店安全，去藍店會有危險。長遠落去至少係零售層面可以將中資趕盡殺絕!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"7e4b5b1d8b783b7afb44cb3c56de9f232a6132a6","tid":1624341,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8dd34036236f84465373d03b8089f4daad7bc37","tid":1624341,"uid":268122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}